<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VetGo Prototipo V7 - Tracking GPS y Flujo Corregido</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['"Noto Sans"', 'sans-serif'],
                        body: ['"Satoshi"', 'sans-serif'],
                        headline: ['"Safiro"', 'sans-serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/satoshi');
        
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 10px; }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

        .sidebar-expanded { width: 260px; }
        .sidebar-collapsed { width: 88px; }
        .sidebar-text { transition: opacity 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
        .sidebar-collapsed .sidebar-text { opacity: 0; display: none; }

        .main-expanded { margin-left: 308px; }
        .main-collapsed { margin-left: 136px; }
        
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; }
        .font-body { font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif; }
        .font-headline { font-family: 'Satoshi', sans-serif; }

        .bg-map-pattern {
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#9ca3af 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
        }

        /* Animación personalizada para la ruta del mapa */
        .dash-anim {
            stroke-dasharray: 10;
            animation: dash 20s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes dash {
            to { stroke-dashoffset: -1000; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#F1F1F1] text-[#333333] min-h-screen relative overflow-x-hidden">

    <div id="auth-wrapper" class="block w-full min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6 bg-[#1E3A8A]">
        
        <div id="auth-login" class="bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl p-12 max-w-[450px] w-full flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-[#1E3A8A]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[40px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">pets</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="font-headline text-[32px] text-[#1E3A8A] mb-2">Bienvenido a VetGo</h1>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-[#888888] mb-8 text-center">Tu veterinario, donde está tu mascota.</p>
            
            <div class="w-full space-y-4 mb-8">
                <div>
                    <label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Correo electrónico</label>
                    <input type="email" value="valentina@ejemplo.com" class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] font-sans text-[14px] text-[#333333] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1E3A8A] focus:outline-none">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Contraseña</label>
                    <input type="password" value="********" class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] font-sans text-[14px] text-[#333333] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1E3A8A] focus:outline-none">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <button onclick="doLogin()" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#1E3A8A] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase hover:bg-[#172b66] transition-colors shadow-md mb-4">
                INICIAR SESIÓN
            </button>
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-role-select')" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] border border-[#1E3A8A] text-[#1E3A8A] bg-transparent font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase hover:bg-[#1E3A8A]/5 transition-colors">
                CREAR UNA CUENTA
            </button>
        </div>

        <div id="auth-role-select" class="hidden bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl p-12 max-w-[600px] w-full flex flex-col items-center">
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-login')" class="self-start text-[#888888] hover:text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span></button>
            <h1 class="font-headline text-[32px] text-[#1E3A8A] mb-2">Únete a VetGo</h1>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-[#888888] mb-8 text-center">¿Cómo deseas usar la plataforma?</p>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 w-full mb-8">
                <div onclick="switchAuth('auth-register-client-1')" class="cursor-pointer border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#1E3A8A] rounded-[24px] p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#1E3A8A]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#1E3A8A] mb-4">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">face</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-headline text-[20px] text-[#333333] mb-2">Dueño de Mascota</span>
                    <span class="font-sans text-[12px] text-[#888888]">Busco atención domiciliaria y digitalizar el historial.</span>
                </div>
                <div onclick="switchAuth('auth-register-vet-1')" class="cursor-pointer border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-[#1E3A8A] rounded-[24px] p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-colors">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#F39C12]/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#F39C12] mb-4">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[32px]">medical_services</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-headline text-[20px] text-[#333333] mb-2">Profesional (MVZ)</span>
                    <span class="font-sans text-[12px] text-[#888888]">Quiero ofrecer mis servicios y gestionar mis consultas.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="auth-register-client-1" class="hidden bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl p-12 max-w-[500px] w-full flex flex-col">
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-role-select')" class="self-start text-[#888888] hover:text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span></button>
            <h1 class="font-headline text-[32px] text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6">Tus datos personales</h1>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                <div><label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Nombre completo</label><input type="text" class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1E3A8A] outline-none"></div>
            </div>
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-register-client-2')" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#1E3A8A] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase hover:bg-[#172b66] transition-colors">SIGUIENTE</button>
        </div>
        <div id="auth-register-client-2" class="hidden bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl p-12 max-w-[500px] w-full flex flex-col">
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-register-client-1')" class="self-start text-[#888888] hover:text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span></button>
            <h1 class="font-headline text-[32px] text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6">Tu primera mascota</h1>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                <div><label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Nombre de la mascota</label><input type="text" class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1E3A8A] outline-none"></div>
            </div>
            <button onclick="doLogin()" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#2ECC71] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase hover:bg-[#27ae60] transition-colors">CREAR CUENTA VETGO</button>
        </div>

        <div id="auth-register-vet-1" class="hidden bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl p-12 max-w-[500px] w-full flex flex-col">
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-role-select')" class="self-start text-[#888888] hover:text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span></button>
            <span class="font-body text-[12px] text-[#888888] tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Paso 1 de 2</span>
            <h1 class="font-headline text-[32px] text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6">Perfil Profesional</h1>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                <div>
                    <label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Nombre completo (MVZ)</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Ej. Dr. Andrés Gómez" class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1E3A8A] outline-none">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Especialidad principal</label>
                    <select class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] bg-white focus:outline-none">
                        <option>Generalista</option>
                        <option>Dermatología</option>
                        <option>Especialista Felinos</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-register-vet-2')" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#1E3A8A] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase hover:bg-[#172b66] transition-colors">SIGUIENTE</button>
        </div>

        <div id="auth-register-vet-2" class="hidden bg-white rounded-[32px] shadow-2xl p-12 max-w-[500px] w-full flex flex-col">
            <button onclick="switchAuth('auth-register-vet-1')" class="self-start text-[#888888] hover:text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span></button>
            <span class="font-body text-[12px] text-[#888888] tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Verificación</span>
            <h1 class="font-headline text-[32px] text-[#1E3A8A] mb-6">Documentación Legal</h1>
            <p class="font-sans text-[12px] text-[#888888] mb-6">Para garantizar la seguridad, necesitamos validar tus credenciales como especialista.</p>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
                <div>
                    <label class="block font-sans text-[14px] text-[#3C3C3C] mb-2 pl-2">Número de Tarjeta Profesional</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Ej. 12345-MVZ" class="w-full h-[52px] px-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-[200px] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1E3A8A] outline-none">
                </div>
                <div class="w-full p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-[#1E3A8A]/50 bg-[#1E3A8A]/5 rounded-[24px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#1E3A8A]/10 transition-colors">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#1E3A8A] text-[32px] mb-2">cloud_upload</span>
                    <span class="font-body text-[14px] font-medium text-[#1E3A8A]">Sube tu Diploma o Tarjeta Profesional</span>
                    <span class="font-sans text-[12px] text-[#888888] mt-1">Formatos: JPG, PNG, PDF</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <button onclick="doLogin('vet')" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#2ECC71] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase hover:bg-[#27ae60] transition-colors shadow-md">
                ENVIAR A VERIFICACIÓN
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div id="app-wrapper" class="hidden">
        
        <aside id="sidebar" class="sidebar-expanded h-[calc(100vh-48px)] fixed left-[24px] top-[24px] bg-[#333333] rounded-[32px] py-[32px] flex flex-col z-40 transition-all duration-300 overflow-x-hidden shadow-lg">
            <button onclick="toggleSidebar()" class="absolute -right-3 top-[48px] w-8 h-8 bg-[#2A2A2A] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-[#4A4A4A] text-white hover:bg-[#4A4A4A] transition-colors z-10 shadow-md">
                <span id="sidebar-icon" class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]">chevron_left</span>
            </button>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white mb-10 px-[24px] cursor-pointer" onclick="switchView('dashboard-view')">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[28px] flex-shrink-0" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1; color: #60A5FA;">pets</span>
                <span class="font-bold text-[22px] tracking-wide sidebar-text">VetGo</span>
            </div>
            
            <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2 flex-1 font-sans text-[16px] font-normal text-white overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar px-[16px]">
                <a class="client-menu-item flex items-center gap-4 px-3 py-3 text-white hover:bg-white/10 rounded-[200px] transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="switchView('dashboard-view')">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px] flex-shrink-0" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">home</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-text">Inicio</span>
                </a>
                
                <a class="client-menu-item flex items-center gap-4 px-3 py-3 text-white hover:bg-white/10 rounded-[200px] transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="switchView('pets-list-view')">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px] flex-shrink-0" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">pets</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-text">Mascotas</span>
                </a>

                <a onclick="startVetRegistration()" class="client-menu-item flex items-center gap-4 px-3 py-3 text-[#F39C12] hover:bg-[#F39C12]/10 rounded-[200px] transition-colors mt-6 cursor-pointer border border-transparent hover:border-[#F39C12]/30">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px] flex-shrink-0" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">work</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-text font-medium text-[14px]">Únete como Profesional</span>
                </a>

                <a class="vet-menu-item hidden flex items-center gap-4 px-3 py-3 text-[#60A5FA] bg-[#1E3A8A]/30 rounded-[200px] transition-colors cursor-pointer">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px] flex-shrink-0" style="font-variation-settings: 'wght' 300;">calendar_month</span>
                    <span class="sidebar-text font-medium">Mi Agenda</span>
                </a>
            </nav>
            
            <div class="mt-auto flex flex-col items-stretch gap-2 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 px-[16px]">
                
                <button onclick="toggleAppMode()" id="mode-toggle-btn" class="w-full bg-[#1E3A8A]/20 text-[#60A5FA] border border-[#1E3A8A] rounded-[200px] py-2 px-4 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 font-body text-[12px] font-bold uppercase hover:bg-[#1E3A8A]/40 transition-colors sidebar-text mb-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">swap_horiz</span>
                    <span id="mode-toggle-text">Cambiar a Especialista</span>
                </button>

                <button class="w-full bg-white text-[#333333] rounded-[200px] py-3 px-4 flex justify-between items-center font-sans text-[16px] font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors sidebar-text">
                    <span class="truncate pr-2 text-[14px]">Valentina Rodríguez</span>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">expand_more</span>
                </button>
                <button onclick="doLogout()" class="w-full bg-transparent text-[#888888] rounded-[200px] py-2 px-4 flex justify-center items-center gap-2 font-body text-[12px] font-bold uppercase hover:text-white transition-colors sidebar-text mt-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">logout</span>
                    <span>Cerrar Sesión</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main id="main-content" class="main-expanded transition-all duration-300 p-8 pb-24 relative">
            
            <div id="dashboard-view" class="view-section block">
                <div class="flex w-full gap-8 mb-10">
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-[500px] flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="bg-[#333333] rounded-[24px] px-[32px] py-[24px] flex flex-col justify-center shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.08)] flex-1">
                            <span class="text-[#F1F1F1]/80 font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">HOLA, VALENTINA</span>
                            <h1 class="text-[#F1F1F1] font-headline text-[40px] leading-[40px] m-0">Salud en Casa</h1>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-4 w-full items-stretch">
                            <button onclick="openRequestModal()" class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#1E3A8A] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase flex items-center justify-center gap-[10px] hover:bg-[#172b66] transition-colors shadow-sm">
                                PEDIR VETERINARIO <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">note_add</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-[#FFFFFF] rounded-[24px] px-[40px] py-[32px] shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] flex-1 flex gap-16 items-center justify-center relative">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-center text-center">
                            <span class="text-[#3C3C3C] font-body text-[16px] font-medium uppercase">Mascotas</span>
                            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                                <span class="text-[#2ECC71] font-headline text-[64px] leading-[50px]">2</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-px h-[80px] bg-gray-100"></div> 
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center text-center">
                            <span class="text-[#3C3C3C] font-body text-[16px] font-medium uppercase">Estado General</span>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#1E3A8A]/10 border border-[#1E3A8A]/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-[200px]">
                                    <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#1E3A8A] animate-pulse"></div>
                                    <span class="font-body text-[14px] font-bold uppercase text-[#1E3A8A] tracking-wider">PROTEGIDAS</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="pets-list-view" class="view-section hidden">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-10">
                    <h1 class="text-[#333333] font-headline text-[40px] leading-[40px] m-0">Mis Mascotas</h1>
                    <button onclick="switchView('pet-add-view')" class="h-[48px] px-[24px] rounded-[200px] bg-[#1E3A8A] text-[#FFFFFF] font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-[#172b66] transition-colors shadow-md">
                        AÑADIR MASCOTA <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">add_circle</span>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
                    <div onclick="switchView('pet-profile-view')" class="cursor-pointer bg-[#FFFFFF] rounded-[24px] p-8 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] flex items-center justify-between border border-gray-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow">
                        <div class="max-w-[60%] w-full">
                            <span class="font-body text-[12px] font-medium uppercase text-[#888888] mb-2 block tracking-widest">GATA PERSA</span>
                            <h3 class="font-headline text-[28px] text-[#333333] mb-3">Luna</h3>
                            <p class="font-body text-[14px] font-normal text-[#1E3A8A] font-medium leading-relaxed">Ver ficha médica e historial ></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-[120px] h-[120px] bg-[#1E3A8A]/5 text-[#1E3A8A] rounded-full border border-[#1E3A8A]/20 flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-inner overflow-hidden">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[48px]">pets</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cursor-pointer bg-[#FFFFFF] rounded-[24px] p-8 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] flex items-center justify-between border border-gray-50 hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow">
                        <div class="max-w-[60%] w-full">
                            <span class="font-body text-[12px] font-medium uppercase text-[#888888] mb-2 block tracking-widest">GOLDEN RETRIEVER</span>
                            <h3 class="font-headline text-[28px] text-[#333333] mb-3">Thor</h3>
                            <p class="font-body text-[14px] font-normal text-[#1E3A8A] font-medium leading-relaxed">Ver ficha médica e historial ></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-[120px] h-[120px] bg-gray-100 text-[#888888] rounded-full border border-gray-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-inner overflow-hidden">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[48px]">pets</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="vet-dashboard-view" class="view-section hidden">
                <div class="flex w-full gap-8 mb-10">
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-[500px] flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="bg-[#1E3A8A] rounded-[24px] px-[32px] py-[24px] flex flex-col justify-center shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.15)] flex-1 text-white border border-[#172b66]">
                            <span class="text-white/70 font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">PANEL PROFESIONAL</span>
                            <h1 class="text-white font-headline text-[40px] leading-[40px] m-0">Dr. Mendoza</h1>
                        </div>
                        <button class="w-full h-[48px] rounded-[200px] border border-[#1E3A8A] text-[#1E3A8A] bg-white font-body text-[14px] font-medium uppercase flex items-center justify-center gap-[10px] hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors shadow-sm">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#2ECC71] animate-pulse"></div>
                            DISPONIBLE PARA CONSULTAS
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6 mt-10">
                    <h2 class="text-[#333333] font-headline text-[32px] mb-2">Próximas Visitas Asignadas</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[24px] border-2 border-[#1E3A8A] shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.08)] flex justify-between items-center relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[200px] bg-map-pattern opacity-50 border-l border-gray-100"></div>
